lead_paragraph: LeBron James had 21 points and nine assists and forward Kevin Love had 21 points and 11 rebounds in the Cleveland Cavaliers' 115-93 victory over the Phoenix Suns.

headline.print_headline: James, Love Carry Cavaliers Past Suns
